snippet.title: Hunt and Score - (1978) - Atari 2600 - WIN!
snippet.description:
Atari © 1978
[Console] Atari 2600
Emulator: STELLA 4.6.1

Concentration.... again... oh my goodness... At first they were flashing all these numbers and I thought that was so distracting... not sure why they couldn't put a little number on the boxes - but the switching is better than typical Atari "flashing" when too many sprites are on screen.  in ANY case, I'm so tired of concentration I can't concentrate anymore.  I still managed to beat the 30 tiles with just 11 misses.
